Catalog data sources
====================

The deep-sky object data embedded under `src/data/{messier,ngc,ic,aliases}.csv`
is derived from the OpenNGC catalogue at:

    https://github.com/mattiaverga/OpenNGC

Specifically, `database_files/NGC.csv` was converted into the four files
in this directory by the one-shot script preserved at
`crates/rp-catalog/scripts/openngc_to_catalog.py`. Only the columns
needed for `resolve_target` (canonical name, object type, ICRS RA/Dec,
visual or B magnitude, major-axis size) were retained; the openNGC
"common names" column populated `aliases.csv`.

